# Quote Generator with History ✨

A Flask web application that fetches random quotes from an external API and stores them in a database as history.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Get random quotes from API
- Store quote history in SQLite database
- Simple and clean UI

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML
- CSS
- Requests API

